text: John McKone (3 October 1835 - 7 August 1882) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1855/56 and 1857/58. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1835 births Category:1882 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
